<topic id="drag_and_drop_paste_with_custom_resources">
  <title>Customizing the Smart Paste Mapping</title>
  <body>
    <p>The <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/smart-paste-support.html"
        format="html" scope="external"><i>Smart Paste</i> feature</xref> in <ph keyref="product"/>
      preserves certain style and structure information when copying content and pasting it into XML
      documents. It is also possible to <xref
        href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/author-customize-smart-paste.html"
        format="html" scope="external">customize the mapping for the <i>Smart Paste</i>
        mechanism</xref>.</p>
    <p>If you want full control over this behavior, there are also <xref
        href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/dg-drop-paste-handler.html"
        format="html" scope="external">Java extensions that can be customized</xref>.</p>
  </body>
</topic>
